01:30:28.160 --> 01:30:29.990
economic theory?

01:30:29.990 --> 01:30:31.740
And if they did,
couldn't we solve a lot

01:30:31.740 --> 01:30:33.083
of these problems a lot better?

01:30:33.083 --> 01:30:34.010
[LAUGHS] [INAUDIBLE].

