01:30:59.640 --> 01:31:01.190
supply economic theory.

01:31:01.190 --> 01:31:03.380
AUDIENCE: Well, if
I make a comment--

01:31:03.380 --> 01:31:07.053
Alberto, for those
watching at home--

01:31:07.053 --> 01:31:08.720
the thing that's been
really jumping out

01:31:08.720 --> 01:31:10.345
at me when we talked
about it earlier--

01:31:10.345 --> 01:31:14.030
sort of like the big old beast
of the military industrial

01:31:14.030 --> 01:31:16.400
complex, which from
my understanding

01:31:16.400 --> 01:31:18.470
thrives not on
radical innovation.

01:31:18.470 --> 01:31:20.540
They really love the
incremental thing

01:31:20.540 --> 01:31:22.580
because it can suck
out as much money

01:31:22.580 --> 01:31:24.420
as they can from the government.

01:31:24.420 --> 01:31:26.762
