01:31:28.970 --> 01:31:31.420
money in funding of
that whole business,

01:31:31.420 --> 01:31:33.320
that's why we're
stuck in the 1950s

01:31:33.320 --> 01:31:36.015
because that's the system
that works best for them.

01:31:36.015 --> 01:31:38.000
But to go back to what
Rasheed said, I think--

01:31:38.000 --> 01:31:38.720
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN:
So Alberto, I'd

01:31:38.720 --> 01:31:40.532
contest with you
because I think it's

01:31:40.532 --> 01:31:42.740
fair to say that the military
has brought on actually

01:31:42.740 --> 01:31:44.600
most of the big
radical innovation

01:31:44.600 --> 01:31:47.385
waves of the second
half of the 19th.

01:31:47.385 --> 01:31:48.260
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

01:31:48.260 --> 01:31:50.010
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN:
