01:31:52.855 --> 01:31:54.980
AUDIENCE: What's coming
out the F-35, I don't know.

01:31:54.980 --> 01:31:55.600
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN:
Yeah, what's coming--

01:31:55.600 --> 01:31:57.225
I don't know what's
coming out of that.

01:31:57.225 --> 01:31:58.740
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

01:31:58.740 --> 01:32:02.210
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE] Also
Intel is funded originally

01:32:02.210 --> 01:32:03.440
by government.

01:32:03.440 --> 01:32:05.020
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

01:32:05.020 --> 01:32:06.260
AUDIENCE: Maybe I'm wrong.

01:32:06.260 --> 01:32:08.385
WILLIAM BONVILLIAN: No,
but it's a very good point.

01:32:08.385 --> 01:32:09.980
And I think the
answer is that there's

01:32:09.980 --> 01:32:12.140
different forces in the
military and there's

01:32:12.140 --> 01:32:13.700
huge conservative
forces that want

01:32:13.700 --> 01:32:18.590
to perpetuate their
existing operating systems.

01:32:18.590 --> 01:32:22.460
And it's actually hard to
do disruptive innovation

01:32:22.460 --> 01:32:25.440
