01:32:25.440 --> 01:32:29.060
So I think this play out
between how you bring innovation

01:32:29.060 --> 01:32:32.540
into a legacy sector-- which
the military has actually solved

01:32:32.540 --> 01:32:34.550
a few times--

01:32:34.550 --> 01:32:37.693
is kind of an interesting
idea, and we'll

01:32:37.693 --> 01:32:39.360
keep playing with
this idea as we go on.

01:32:39.360 --> 01:32:43.990
So yes, the military has been
able to launch disruptive

01:32:43.990 --> 01:32:48.010
innovation, but overall it's a
legacy sector and a lot of it

01:32:48.010 --> 01:32:51.130
is resistant to innovation
just as you suggest.

01:32:51.130 --> 01:32:54.225
So it's a very
interesting balance.

